otherwise, here are the enums I can think of:

~~~
        DELETE, // success
        DELETE_NOT_FOUND, // model does not exist
        DELETE_ERROR, // other errors, e.g. permission denied

        FETCH, // success
        FETCH_ALREADY_EXISTS, // model already exists
        FETCH_NOT_FOUND, // model not found
        FETCH_ERROR, // other errors

        UPLOAD, // success
        UPLOAD_ALREADY_EXISTS, // model already exists
        UPLOAD_ERROR // other errors
~~~
